  "3337980": {
    "name": "伊瓦亚米 - 迷雾之摇篮",
    "steam_appid": 3337980,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >幽灵之城伊瓦亚米被迷雾笼罩，扭曲着街道，模糊着记忆，侵蚀着踏入者的心智。新闻系学生辛西娅·森山与三位朋友决定前去调查，但在一场突如其来的车祸后，她孤身一人。为了找回他们，她必须踏上被迷雾笼罩的街道——但等待她的，将比迷路更加可怕。 </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337980/extras/da44df9a4e8cd2c450e01dce2d666e4a.poster.avif?t=1759977579\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337980/extras/da44df9a4e8cd2c450e01dce2d666e4a.webm?t=1759977579\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337980/extras/da44df9a4e8cd2c450e01dce2d666e4a.mp4?t=1759977579\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >一座会呼吸的城市</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >穿行伊瓦亚米的旅程充满了恐惧与脆弱。城市仿佛有生命一般，不断改变道路，将真相隐藏在上锁的门、损坏的机械与遗忘的墙壁上刻下的谜语之后。每一次探索都伴随着风险，而这些风险一步步将辛西娅拉向以她的恐惧为食的深处。这里的每一刻都弥漫着令人不安的气息——那种“她并不孤单”的感觉。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337980/extras/c478784990c1185042e43ce221b38252.poster.avif?t=1759977579\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337980/extras/c478784990c1185042e43ce221b38252.webm?t=1759977579\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337980/extras/c478784990c1185042e43ce221b38252.mp4?t=1759977579\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >在街道上生存</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >怪物，这些昔日之影，游荡在街道间，散布着毒雾，迫使你留意每一步、每一个声音与呼吸，才能活下去。辛西娅唯一的武器，是她的智慧、责任感，以及一路上找到的几件脆弱工具。灯光闪烁，地图误导，街道在脚下变化，安全与绝望之间的界限在每个转角愈发逼仄。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337980/extras/036f9466f4dfc37d370675268a2d3ce4.poster.avif?t=1759977579\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337980/extras/036f9466f4dfc37d370675268a2d3ce4.webm?t=1759977579\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337980/extras/036f9466f4dfc37d370675268a2d3ce4.mp4?t=1759977579\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >沉浸于氛围之中</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >伊瓦亚米不只是背景——它是塑造一切的“存在”。一些地方许诺庇护，却是陷阱；另一些地方让你直面腐朽、仪式，以及早已消逝的生命残迹。一条街的寂静令人窒息，远方的声响却在另一条街引导你前行。每个角落都蕴藏着历史与威胁，让你怀疑这座城市是在揭示秘密……还是将你引向更深的迷雾。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337980/extras/b9b1b15b8047cd53c61b62e951bb43a8.poster.avif?t=1759977579\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337980/extras/b9b1b15b8047cd53c61b62e951bb43a8.webm?t=1759977579\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337980/extras/b9b1b15b8047cd53c61b62e951bb43a8.mp4?t=1759977579\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >支离破碎的人们</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >她的朋友们不仅是拯救目标，更是被迷雾扭曲的脆弱生命。他们的性格被侵蚀，视角发生变化，展现出辛西娅从未见过的一面。将他们重新聚集在一起，既是逃离伊瓦亚米，也是辛西娅守护人性的过程。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337980/extras/647b0a6a99363158bb55c55be23f1a06.poster.avif?t=1759977579\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337980/extras/647b0a6a99363158bb55c55be23f1a06.webm?t=1759977579\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337980/extras/647b0a6a99363158bb55c55be23f1a06.mp4?t=1759977579\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >超过8小时的心理恐怖生存与探索故事。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >PS1/PS2复古风格与动漫角色设计相结合。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >会根据辛西娅的压力变化而动态反应的配乐。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过谜题、笔记和阴森地点展开的环境叙事。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >多重结局决定辛西娅和朋友们是逃脱……还是直面迷雾的起源。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337980/extras/323e69d36727057dbbd9777edcbfc187.poster.avif?t=1759977579\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337980/extras/323e69d36727057dbbd9777edcbfc187.webm?t=1759977579\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337980/extras/323e69d36727057dbbd9777edcbfc187.mp4?t=1759977579\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >辛西娅能否在伊瓦亚米中生存下来，揭开朋友们的命运？ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一个选择都可能是最后的抉择。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
    "supported_languages": "英语, 葡萄牙语 - 巴西, 法语, 德语, 西班牙语 - 西班牙, 韩语, 葡萄牙语 - 葡萄牙, 俄语, 简体中文, 西班牙语 - 拉丁美洲",
